thread.title: Soap | EastEnders

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Soap | EastEnders
text: Well! What about that Fatboy and Donna then? Do we have a new burgeoning romance on the Square? Doesn't look like it I'm afraid as Fatboy admits to Tamwar tonight that Donna is just a friend. Will Donna feel the same? Although she may have enough on her plate tonight as she discovers Les in Claudette's living room. Also tonight, Shabnam bonds with Jade and takes her to the park, but she is soon spotted by Stacey, while elsewhere Kathy ignores Gavin's calls as she and Ben attempt to come up with a plan to get more money.
